 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Poison-point:

    Whenever a move makes contact 
  with this Pokémon, the move's 
  user has a 30% chance of being 
  poisoned.

  Sniper:

    This Pokémon inflicts triple 
  damage with critical hits, rather 
  than the usual double damage.

  Damp:

    While this Pokémon is in battle, 
  self destruct and explosion will 
  fail and aftermath will not take 
  effect.


